  <brief_title>Study Evaluating The Potential Effect Of Rifampin On The Pharmacokinetics Of Neratinib</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study to Examine the Potential Effect of Rifampin on the Pharmacokinetics of Neratinib When Administered Concomitantly to Healthy Subjects</official_title>
