  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to examine whether co-administration of rifampin with neratinib
      has an effect on the pharmacokinetics (how the body absorbs, distributes, metabolizes and/or
      excretes) of neratinib.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
